# Transformail Flask Application

The Transformail Flask Application is a web-based tool that allows you to convert Salesforce templates to Simon templates. It utilizes the Flask framework and provides a user-friendly interface for uploading Salesforce templates, converting them to Simon templates using Jinja2, and downloading the converted templates.

## Features

- Upload Salesforce templates in SML format.
- Convert SML templates to Jinja2 format using predefined conversion patterns.
- Download the converted Jinja2 templates.

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

   ```shell
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/transformail-flask-app.git

Change into the project directory:
    -- cd transformail-flask-app

create venv :
   -- py -3 -m venv venv

   -- venv\Scripts\activate

Install the required dependencies:
    -- pip install -r requirements.txt
Usage
Start the Flask application:
    -- python app.py
Open your web browser and navigate to http://localhost:5000.

Upload a Salesforce template in SML format using the provided form.

Click the "Convert" button to convert the template to Jinja2 format.

Once the conversion is complete, you can download the converted template by clicking the "Download Converted Template" button.

